課程概述 Course Description
       癌症為國人死亡原因首位，本課程以癌症為主要研究模式，著重於癌症病人之抑癌基因、致癌基因變異研究，這些變異分析包括基突變、染色體套數變異、基因多型性分析、表遺傳變異分析；另外，發展新穎癌症治療藥物之細胞及動物模式亦為研究之重點。 

課程學習目標 Course Objectives    
	    使同學瞭解癌症細胞及臨床特徵，並探討分子致癌機制。    

課程進度 Course Outline


週次 Week進度說明 Progress Description
1Cancer biology: basis ideas I2Cancer biology: basis ideas II3Natural history: the life of a cancer4What is cancer? / Pathology: defining a neoplasm5Oncogenes, repressor genes and virus6Chemical and radiation carcinogenesis7Mutations, DNA repair and genetic instability8Familial cancers9Growth: proliferation, death and differentiation10Responding to the environment: signal transduction11Invasion and metastasis12Principle of cancer treatment13Tumor immunology and immunotherapy14Cancer prevention / Epidemiology15Student presentation16Student presentation17Student presentation18Student presentation 

　以上每週進度教師可依上課情況做適度調整。The schedule may be subject to change.


